source.name: Amount by Zip Code Descending
source.description: Catholic Charities serves more than 58,000 people each year at more than 60 sites across Long Island, NY. Thousands were helped by Catholic Charities in the wake of Hurricane Sandy. This data set shows the distribution of dollars by this organization throughout Long Island by zip code, town and the number of people assisted.
